p: The main effects of irradiance showed a reduction of germling growth rate from high irradiance intensity (7.8% h -1) to low irradiance intensity (6.5% h -1), a 14.3% drop ( Fig 5C). This decrease was clearer under the combination of control CO 2 and ambient temperature (Figs 5D and 4E, one-way ANOVA, p = 0.032) ( S4 Table).
